title: Grateful Dead Live at Hampton Coliseum on 1986-03-19
lineage: Nakamichi CR7A>Lucid AD9624>Fostex D5>DAT>Tascam DA20MKII>Tascam CDRW700>CDR>Wavelab 6>CDWave>Flac Frontend(Level 6); Recording by DATBRAD; Master cassette transfer to DAT by Mark Lynn; DAT to CDR and conversion to wav>flac by DATBRAD
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Stagger Lee, CC Rider, Cold Rain & Snow-> Beat It On Down The Line-> Big Railroad Blues-> Looks Like Rain-> Visions Of Johanna-> The Music Never Stopped-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Truckin'-> Black Peter-> Around & Around
